reviewText:
This movie will keep you bouncing and jumping with laughter because it has that tendency of comedy to keep you going. As an Extra in the last church scene wearing my Alfro natural hair,all the cast had fun in putting this comedy
movie together.
I gave this simple movie 5 stars because its funny; and I'm in the movie...(smile) I had a great time shooting this film. The Producers were fantastic and kind and treated the actors like GOLD.
We watched it just to see Michael Kan in this movie, so probably slightly biased by that. It's a style of comedy that normally wouldn't appeal, but we were entertained. Fun night!

Flat out buffoonery, yet another black film embarrassing to the black race just like Soul Plane, Ride & Cookout.  What a waste of film, actor's time & the money it took to produce this foolishness.  From the very beginning it started off ridiculous.
I RENTED THIS MOVIE FROM REDBOX AND I AN VERY PLEASED.  THIS MOVIE WILL KEEP YOU LAUGHING FROM BEGINNING TO END.  IF YOUR LOOKING FOR A FUNNY MOVIE , rent or buy this.

Ok first of all this movie  is one of the funniest films I have seen since Fridays  . Its star studded and well produced . Charlie murphy and AL Shearer  are both funny apart but crazy  in tandem .I would recommend this to anyone who enjoys a good laugh . This is a classic well worth the price
 PS KIM WHITLY and JOHN WITHERSPON is a beast with it !!!!
I loved this movie. It's low budget, but well-made. Charlie Murphy and Al Shearer are so funny. Their antics are hysterical. Some parts had me laughing till I couldn't breath.
